name: Unidentified_female_Togorian
content: This individual was a female Togorian and the innkeeper of the Soft Landings Inn, an inn on the planet Coruscant. In 43 BBY, Jedi Master Qui-Gon Jinn and his Padawan Obi-Wan Kenobi went to the Soft Landings Inn looking for the bounty hunter Ona Nobis. The innkeeper admitted the Jedi into the inn without any trouble.
